text: Sheriff Woody is the main character of the movies Toy Story, Toy Story 2, Toy Story 3 and Toy Story 4. he is voiced by Tom Hanks in the films while his brother Jim Hanks voices him in the video games, merchandise, and attractions. ==Appearances== ===Movies=== * Toy Story (1995) * Toy Story 2 (1999) * Toy Story 3 (2010) * Toy Story 4 (2019) Category:Fictional characters introduced in 1995 Category:Kingdom Hearts characters Category:Toy Story characters Category:Animated movie characters
title: Woody (Toy Story)
